ade manifest to you [in terms of law], might cause you hardship; for, if you should ask about them while the Qur'an is being revealed, they might [indeed] be made manifest to you [as laws]. God has absolved [you from any obligation] in this respect: for God is much-forgiving, forbearing.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/770.mp3","surahId":5,"words":[{"id":71473,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_101_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":71474,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_101_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":71475,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/005_101_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":71476,"position":4,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/005_101_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":71477,"position":5,"arabic":"تَسْـَٔلُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা প্রশ্ন করো","audioUrl":"wbw/005_101_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":71478,"position":6,"arabic":"عَنْ","translation":"সম্পর্কে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_101_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":71479,"position":7,"arabic":"أَشْيَآءَ","translation":"(এমন) বিষয়াদি","audioUrl":"wbw/005_101_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":71480,"position":8,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/005_101_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":71481,"position":9,"arabic":"تُبْدَ","translation":"প্রকাশ করা হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/005_101_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":71482,"position":10,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","translation":"জন্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_101_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":71483,"position":11,"arabic":"تَسُؤْكُمْ","translation":"খারাপ লাগবে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_101_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":71484,"position":12,"arabic":"وَإِن","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/005_101_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":71485,"position":13,"arabic":"تَسْـَٔلُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা প্রশ্ন করো","audioU